<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:07:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>五角大楼称，乌克兰可能出于自卫而向俄罗斯深处发射美国提供的导弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-may-fire-us-provided-missiles-deeper-into-russia-in-self-defense-pentagon-says/articleshow/111176645.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111176645.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五角大楼授权乌克兰出于自卫目的使用美国远程导弹打击俄罗斯目标，范围扩展到哈尔科夫以外。拜登总统放宽了对美国弹药的限制，以帮助乌克兰抵御俄罗斯对乌克兰领土的持续袭击，为基辅提供更大的灵活性来应对当前前线战斗之外的威胁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:00:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-may-fire-us-provided-missiles-deeper-into-russia-in-self-defense-pentagon-says/articleshow/111176645.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国威胁对“顽固”台独分子判处死刑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-threatens-death-penalty-for-diehard-taiwan-separatists/articleshow/111176612.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111176612.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国考虑对“顽固”台独活动人士判处死刑，导致赖清德总统就职以来的紧张局势升级。指导方针要求严惩分裂分子，以捍卫国家主权。台湾政府正在评估新规则，因为总统赖清德在与中国的对话中面临拒绝。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 21:47:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-threatens-death-penalty-for-diehard-taiwan-separatists/articleshow/111176612.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈里王子“讨厌酒店，访问英国时会乔装打扮”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-hates-hotels-and-wears-a-disguise-on-uk-visits/articleshow/111176608.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111176608.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 21:51:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-hates-hotels-and-wears-a-disguise-on-uk-visits/articleshow/111176608.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员描述政府秘密竞标以巩固对约旦河西岸的控制</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-official-describes-secret-government-bid-to-cement-control-of-west-bank/articleshow/111176314.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111176314.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在最近的一次演讲中，有影响力的联盟成员贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇披露了以色列在不正式吞并的情况下巩固对西岸控制的秘密计划，旨在防止其成为巴勒斯坦国的一部分。此举引发了人们对以色列在巴以冲突中对该领土的管理性质的质疑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 20:59:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-official-describes-secret-government-bid-to-cement-control-of-west-bank/articleshow/111176314.cms</guid></item><item><title>比比与美国及本国军队的争执引发了对战争未来的质疑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bibis-spats-with-us-own-military-raise-questions-on-wars-future/articleshow/111176308.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111176308.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在针对哈马斯的战争中面临国内和国际冲突，在应对与军事领导人、联盟伙伴、白宫和拜登政府的挑战时，对战争的未来和他的政治生存提出了质疑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 20:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bibis-spats-with-us-own-military-raise-questions-on-wars-future/articleshow/111176308.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队炮击加沙帐篷营地，造成25人死亡、50人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-forces-shell-tent-camps-in-gaza-killing-25-and-injuring-50/articleshow/111176149.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111176149.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 20:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-forces-shell-tent-camps-in-gaza-killing-25-and-injuring-50/articleshow/111176149.cms</guid></item><item><title>Hindujas 如何成为英国最富有的家族</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/how-hindujas-became-the-richest-family-of-uk/articleshow/111176059.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111176059.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 20:11:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/how-hindujas-became-the-richest-family-of-uk/articleshow/111176059.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿肯色州杂货店发生枪击事件 2人死亡8人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-killed-8-injured-in-shooting-at-grocery-store-in-arkansas/articleshow/111175846.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111175846.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;警方称，周五阿肯色州南部一家杂货店发生枪击事件，造成两人死亡、八人受伤。枪击事件发生在福代斯的疯狂屠夫杂货店。枪手被警察开枪射中后身受重伤。一名执法人员被枪杀，但没有生命危险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:18:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-killed-8-injured-in-shooting-at-grocery-store-in-arkansas/articleshow/111175846.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克有一个秘密孩子，今年早些时候出生：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-has-a-secret-child-born-earlier-this-year-report/articleshow/111175691.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111175691.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据彭博社报道，埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 与 Neuralink 高管 Shivon Zilis 育有一个秘密孩子，后者是马斯克 2021 年出生的双胞胎的母亲，但马斯克和 Zilis 均未证实或发表声明。这使得埃隆·马斯克成为至少 12 个孩子的父亲，报告得出的结论是，这位最富有和“世界上最有权势的人”一直在用他的金钱和职位倡导生育运动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 18:55:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-has-a-secret-child-born-earlier-this-year-report/articleshow/111175691.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦因“亵渎”指控而处以私刑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-lynching-over-blasphemy-claims/articleshow/111175610.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111175610.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 18:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-lynching-over-blasphemy-claims/articleshow/111175610.cms</guid></item><item><title>比尔·马赫陷入“莫迪选举失败”争论：他的最后 5 次声明</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bill-maher-caught-in-modi-lost-election-row-his-last-5-statements/articleshow/111174475.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111174475.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;喜剧演员兼政治评论员比尔·马赫声称纳伦德拉·莫迪在印度大选中惨败，此举激怒了互联网。尽管社交媒体用户要求他坚持关注美国问题，但比尔·马赫却因其有争议且令人震惊的言论而闻名。事实上，他的书名叫《这位喜剧演员所说的会让你震惊》。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 16:54:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bill-maher-caught-in-modi-lost-election-row-his-last-5-statements/articleshow/111174475.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的绿卡承诺不会……：需要知道的 5 件事</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trumps-green-card-promise-not-for-communists-hamas-supporters-5-things-to-know/articleshow/111173493.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111173493.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;如果唐纳德·特朗普就任总统，经过最彻底审查的最有技能的毕业生将有资格获得自动绿卡承诺。特朗普竞选团队国家新闻秘书卡罗琳·莱维特表示，共产主义者、激进伊斯兰主义者、哈马斯支持者、美国仇恨者和公共指控将被排除在外。唐纳德·特朗普早些时候并没有在移民问题上树立良好的先例。他在担任总统之初禁止来自七个以穆斯林为主的国家的旅行者，后来接受了将合法移民减少一半的提议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 15:32:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trumps-green-card-promise-not-for-communists-hamas-supporters-5-things-to-know/articleshow/111173493.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克批评梅琳达·法兰西·盖茨对乔·拜登的支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-criticizes-melinda-french-gates-over-joe-biden-support/articleshow/111172933.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111172933.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马斯克在推文中写道，“盖茨基金会的影响力并不是减少审查的理由。如果有什么不同的话，那就是它需要更多的审查。”他的评论针对的是梅琳达·弗伦奇·盖茨担任联合主席的盖茨基金会所具有的重大政治和慈善影响力。马斯克的言论是对法国盖茨继续支持拜登总统的回应。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:46:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-criticizes-melinda-french-gates-over-joe-biden-support/articleshow/111172933.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京：北约进军亚洲</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nato-moving-into-asia-putin/articleshow/111172904.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111172904.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在越南发表讲话时强调亚太地区需要建立“可靠的安全架构”，并对北约日益关注该地区表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:42:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nato-moving-into-asia-putin/articleshow/111172904.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国最高法院维持联邦家庭暴力持枪禁令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-supreme-court-upholds-federal-domestic-violence-gun-ban/articleshow/111172774.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111172774.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国最高法院周五维持了一项联邦法律，该法律将家庭暴力限制令下的人持有枪支定为犯罪，这将胜利交给了乔·拜登总统的政府，因为在大规模扩大枪支权利后，法官们选择不再进一步扩大枪支权利。 2022年，8比1的裁决推翻了下级法院推翻1994年法律的决定，该法律违反了美国宪法第二修正案“持有和携带武器”的权利。总部位于新奥尔良的美国第五巡回上诉法院得出结论，该措施未能通过最高法院在 2022 年制定的严格测试，该测试要求枪支法“与国家枪支监管的历史传统保持一致”，以符合第二修正案</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-supreme-court-upholds-federal-domestic-violence-gun-ban/articleshow/111172774.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国富有夫妇被指控为海景投毒树木</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/wealthy-us-couple-accused-of-poisoning-trees-for-ocean-view/articleshow/111172773.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111172773.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据福克斯新闻报道，2021 年，圣路易斯基金会前首席执行官阿米莉亚·邦德据称未经丽莎·戈尔曼同意，对她的橡树使用了致命的除草剂特布噻隆。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:33:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/wealthy-us-couple-accused-of-poisoning-trees-for-ocean-view/articleshow/111172773.cms</guid></item><item><title>“梅根·马克尔向维多利亚·贝克汉姆提供免费衣服的请求被宫殿拒绝”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meghan-markles-request-for-free-clothes-from-victoria-beckham-denied-by-palace/articleshow/111172580.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111172580.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;汤姆·鲍尔（Tom Bower）所著的《贝克汉姆之家》一书揭露了梅根·马克尔、哈里王子和贝克汉姆一家之间的紧张关系，这种紧张关系是因怀疑泄露个人建议而引发的，并升级为涉及白金汉宫和大卫·贝克汉姆的对抗。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meghan-markles-request-for-free-clothes-from-victoria-beckham-denied-by-palace/articleshow/111172580.cms</guid></item><item><title>查尔斯国王、泰勒·斯威夫特和现在的巨石阵：“停止石油”如何让抗议活动升级</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/king-charles-taylor-swift-and-now-stonehenge-how-just-stop-oil-is-escalating-protests/articleshow/111172463.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111172463.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;抗议者用橙色油漆瞄准历史悠久的巨石阵纪念碑，以提高人们对气候变化的认识。 “停止石油”活动人士举行示威，呼吁采取紧急行动应对气候危机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:15:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/king-charles-taylor-swift-and-now-stonehenge-how-just-stop-oil-is-escalating-protests/articleshow/111172463.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么乔·拜登在特朗普辩论中选择观众的右侧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/why-joe-biden-chose-audiences-right-side-for-trump-debate/articleshow/111172320.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111172320.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登通过掷硬币赢得了胜利，为即将到来的与唐纳德·特朗普的辩论选择了自己的舞台位置。拜登选择了亚特兰大舞台的左侧，战略性地将自己定位在电视屏幕的右侧，以吸引更多观众的注意力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/why-joe-biden-chose-audiences-right-side-for-trump-debate/articleshow/111172320.cms</guid></item><item><title>比尔·马赫因声称纳伦德拉·莫迪在印度选举中落败而遭到残酷网络攻击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bill-maher-brutally-trolled-for-claiming-narendra-modi-lost-election-in-india/articleshow/111172031.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111172031.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国电视主持人比尔·马赫在一档节目中评论印度大选，称纳伦德拉·莫迪“输掉了选举”。当他在X上发布视频后，社交媒体用户（主要来自印度）对他进行了教育，并提醒他莫迪在赢得选举后第三次成为总理。 “美国主流媒体太愚蠢了。莫迪赢得了选举，比尔。控制住，”一位用户写道。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 13:46:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bill-maher-brutally-trolled-for-claiming-narendra-modi-lost-election-in-india/articleshow/111172031.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>